{"tid":561262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【快活谷夜馬】跑出賽果8、7、2、4！","createTime":"2018-02-15T00:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T00:38:01.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33828df378e3d295546b633383b4e27b084bbef2","tid":561262,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180214/57834908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57834908&d=tC8wHLE06i9okBTfUkldojA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=aecb1c02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57834908&h=962e4e74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180214/57834908</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n谷中這晚（14日）第六場三班1000米，蘇保羅馬房「實力飛駒」夥拍見習騎師黃皓楠一放而回，馬兒季內首度建功，單Win及組合獨贏A1分別派69.5及29.5元。<br />\n<br />\n「實力飛駒」對上一次贏馬評69分，如今跌到67分，加埋用黃皓楠有五磅減，實際僅負110磅仲排埋2檔慳位跑，結果貼住內欄一放絕塵，大勝兩馬位，贏馬姿態相當輕鬆，亦令蘇保羅馬房在近四次賽事內，第三次有馬贏，兼見證騎練季內首度合作數糊。<br />\n今晚頭場賽前全場默哀悼念上周六（10日）大埔公路巴士翻側的馬迷死難者，當日肇事巴士路線為872號。而今晚第六場賽事順序由8號「實力飛駒」、7號「越影」、2號「鄉村輝煌」、4號「大風暴」跑入前四名，即是賽果為8、7、2、4，世事就是這樣巧合！而今場四重彩派四萬九千幾，三T派67萬幾。<br />\n蘇保羅表示「實力飛駒」上季贏馬一仗，由前女見習生蔣嘉琦策騎，都是差不多的贏馬方式，又是排內擋，評分也差不多，今次換上另一位見習騎師黃皓楠，輕磅下放頭走形勢有利，與上季嘉琦贏馬一役差不多。"},{"pid":"8b9a07b4727bc4ac980cbec2220665ce3411a8e6","tid":561262,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"8724 係咪好唔吉利呵?!~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}